WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:07.090
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.090 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 22]

01:15.830 --> 01:16.810
You have to shoulder the responsibility.

01:19.470 --> 01:20.420
You don't have the right to give up.

01:21.440 --> 01:22.370
And you can't throw your life away.

01:27.030 --> 01:28.290
You have to live on

01:28.550 --> 01:31.450
for Yue for thousands of years.

01:32.440 --> 01:33.250
Tongzhou,

01:33.520 --> 01:37.450
I'll leave Yue and Jingwu to you.

01:45.800 --> 01:46.730
You're right.

01:48.520 --> 01:50.060
I am Prince Ying of the Yue State.

01:52.000 --> 01:53.700
I will rescue Jingwu

01:55.160 --> 01:56.450
and

01:58.030 --> 01:59.530
all my people.

02:00.830 --> 02:05.170
I'll never let Tonghe and uncle

02:07.670 --> 02:08.780
down again.

02:18.900 --> 02:19.850
Heaven's justice prevails.

02:21.040 --> 02:22.180
We'll avenge all those

02:22.200 --> 02:22.970
who died unjustly.

03:28.550 --> 03:29.780
That old fool

03:30.520 --> 03:32.530
even infused Burning Flame into his spirit energy

03:32.870 --> 03:35.460
at death's door to ambush me.

03:47.760 --> 03:51.620
They are mostly tied to the Divine Tree.

03:52.480 --> 03:54.020
Whoever gains the Divine Tree

03:54.320 --> 03:57.530
will reign supreme under heaven.

04:00.360 --> 04:01.060
Who's there?

04:01.480 --> 04:02.130
Father.

04:09.710 --> 04:10.250
Father.

04:15.430 --> 04:16.740
What brings you here?

04:19.040 --> 04:21.370
I'm worried about your injuries,

04:21.680 --> 04:23.010
so I decocted medicinal herbs

04:23.760 --> 04:25.500
to purge your poison and restore your strength.

04:26.710 --> 04:28.740
My injuries are trivial.

04:29.390 --> 04:31.450
A few days' meditation will heal me.

04:33.350 --> 04:33.890
Understood.

04:36.470 --> 04:38.370
Have you found Ji Tongzhou?

04:39.440 --> 04:40.180
Not yet.

04:41.000 --> 04:43.100
But I know him well.

04:43.440 --> 04:44.980
He will never leave Duantu.

04:45.440 --> 04:46.130
Rest assured.

04:46.680 --> 04:48.810
I'll capture him by any means.

04:50.080 --> 04:51.210
Can you bring yourself to do it?

04:53.270 --> 04:56.210
I cannot. I love him so deeply,

04:56.880 --> 04:58.420
yet he never sees me.

04:59.320 --> 05:00.130
I will not accept this.

05:00.700 --> 05:02.130
I must subdue him

05:02.710 --> 05:04.100
and make him mine alone.

05:06.390 --> 05:07.810
You promised me once

05:08.580 --> 05:09.770
you would spare his life.

05:10.270 --> 05:11.890
I'll keep my word.

05:12.710 --> 05:13.250
Also,

05:13.910 --> 05:16.010
seize Jiang Lifei and Lei Xiuyuan

05:16.030 --> 05:17.060
and bring them to me.

05:19.340 --> 05:22.250
You want to seek the Divine Tree from...

05:23.900 --> 05:25.890
Yes. I see.

05:26.660 --> 05:30.890
Now prepare yourself to be the Empress of the Yue State.

05:51.790 --> 05:52.890
Lanya set up a mourning hall at the palace gate

05:53.460 --> 05:54.810
and held Crown Prince Ji Jingwu hostage

05:55.020 --> 05:55.980
to force the Yue people to surrender.

05:59.580 --> 06:00.330
I'll scout for news.

06:00.830 --> 06:01.570
Look after Tongzhou.

06:03.980 --> 06:04.570
Wait.

06:07.460 --> 06:08.420
I'm coming with you.

06:08.910 --> 06:09.420
But...

06:09.460 --> 06:09.940
Lifei.

06:14.220 --> 06:16.100
We'll set off together later tonight.

06:32.680 --> 06:34.760
[Mingkun Gate]

06:50.710 --> 06:52.100
Zhijie, wake up.

06:52.560 --> 06:53.330
It's Mingli.

06:54.000 --> 06:54.450
Halt!

07:26.710 --> 07:27.540
Guard your heart meridians!

07:44.390 --> 07:45.450
Zhijie, let's go now.

07:45.910 --> 07:46.660
Mingli, go on ahead.

07:47.350 --> 07:48.300
I'll catch up to you.

08:12.560 --> 08:14.210
The crown prince is an imposter! Escort the Yue Emperor away!

08:21.880 --> 08:22.420
Zhijie,

08:23.590 --> 08:24.300
you know

08:25.150 --> 08:26.300
I had no choice.

08:26.640 --> 08:27.370
I never wanted this.

08:28.270 --> 08:29.540
We grew up side by side.

08:30.590 --> 08:32.420
You won't harm me, will you?

08:38.400 --> 08:38.940
Your Ladyship,

08:46.080 --> 08:47.180
stop while you still can.

09:08.830 --> 09:09.970
Your Ladyship.

09:12.160 --> 09:12.660
Your...

09:20.200 --> 09:20.610
After them!

09:27.350 --> 09:28.060
Search over there.

09:28.710 --> 09:29.570
Check thoroughly.

09:32.920 --> 09:33.610
Head that way.

09:33.920 --> 09:34.420
All right.

09:34.870 --> 09:35.450
Nothing here.

09:35.960 --> 09:36.610
Nothing here.

09:37.110 --> 09:37.570
Search every corner!

09:50.470 --> 09:51.380
We're surrounded by pursuers.

09:51.990 --> 09:52.420
What do we do?

09:52.750 --> 09:53.850
They're after me.

09:54.590 --> 09:55.330
I'll lead them away.

09:55.510 --> 09:55.940
No way.

09:56.350 --> 09:57.380
Your Highness, don't risk yourself.

09:58.750 --> 09:59.570
Leave with the Yue Emperor.

10:00.040 --> 10:01.330
Tongzhou and I will draw them off.

10:01.830 --> 10:02.330
Count me in.

10:11.870 --> 10:12.450
Tongzhou.

10:16.590 --> 10:17.210
Tongzhou. Tongzhou.

10:17.800 --> 10:19.660
Tongzhou.

10:19.870 --> 10:20.260
Keep up!

10:32.750 --> 10:34.060
Miss, please.

10:34.230 --> 10:35.180
Spare some food for me.

10:42.960 --> 10:43.330
Hurry.

10:48.470 --> 10:48.970
Follow me.

10:51.660 --> 10:51.970
Let's go.

11:11.990 --> 11:13.450
Rest easy, you're safe here.

11:21.400 --> 11:22.730
You might show your true face,

11:23.200 --> 11:24.690
so we may repay you later.

11:27.110 --> 11:28.490
Uncle!

11:30.630 --> 11:31.420
Jingwu.

11:33.160 --> 11:33.660
Jingwu.

11:35.230 --> 11:35.690
Jingwu!

11:36.050 --> 11:37.200
[Ji Jingwu]

11:37.750 --> 11:39.380
He's the real Crown Prince.

11:42.040 --> 11:42.940
Then who are you?

11:46.160 --> 11:47.690
I'm Miaoqing, a palace maid

11:48.660 --> 11:49.300
serving His Highness.

11:54.080 --> 11:54.850
You're no maid.

11:55.660 --> 11:56.940
You're a dancer from Yange Hall.

11:57.750 --> 11:59.060
You used Jingwu to get close to us.

11:59.350 --> 12:00.300
What do you want?

12:01.350 --> 12:01.810
Speak!

12:03.230 --> 12:04.850
Uncle, let her go!

12:05.470 --> 12:06.810
She's telling the truth.

12:11.280 --> 12:12.380
She saved us twice.

12:12.830 --> 12:13.850
She means no harm.

12:13.920 --> 12:14.810
Let's hear her out first.

12:22.990 --> 12:24.420
Your Highness still remembers me.

12:24.960 --> 12:26.730
I'm indeed a dancer from Yange Hall.

12:27.040 --> 12:29.090
I've long been grateful for you saving my life.

12:29.540 --> 12:30.420
Later, Match...

12:34.160 --> 12:35.490
Guided by a master,

12:35.870 --> 12:36.810
I came to Yue State

12:37.280 --> 12:38.140
and sneaked into the palace,

12:38.660 --> 12:42.140
thinking I could repay your kindness.

12:45.960 --> 12:48.210
Where did you get this spirit talisman?

12:48.870 --> 12:51.490
Perhaps from that master.

12:51.920 --> 12:54.020
Shortly after he sent me here,

12:54.040 --> 12:56.140
I found it in my robes.

12:56.280 --> 12:58.300
I believe he foresaw my peril

12:58.830 --> 12:59.570
and left it for my protection.

13:01.200 --> 13:02.850
Could it be the Matchmaker at Lugong Town?

13:05.590 --> 13:06.690
I do not know,

13:07.280 --> 13:10.140
but I did meet him under the Matchmaker Tree.

13:10.990 --> 13:11.490
Uncle,

13:12.040 --> 13:14.140
if not for Miaoqing,

13:14.350 --> 13:17.780
I would've been captured by Lanya.

13:18.750 --> 13:21.180
Your Highness, when Dauntu fell under siege,

13:21.660 --> 13:23.140
His Majesty bade me safeguard

13:23.320 --> 13:24.450
the Crown Prince at all costs.

13:26.830 --> 13:27.690
The palace is in utter chaos.

13:28.200 --> 13:29.330
You must protect Jingwu.

13:31.590 --> 13:32.300
Understood.

13:46.200 --> 13:46.730
What are you doing?

13:50.200 --> 13:51.450
My stomach hurts terribly.

13:53.350 --> 13:55.660
Your Ladyship, I shall take His Highness to relieve himself.

13:57.510 --> 13:58.570
Bring him back soon.

13:59.540 --> 14:00.090
Understood.

14:16.040 --> 14:17.260
Now that Lanya has lost her hostage,

14:18.080 --> 14:19.540
no wonder she schemed with a fake prince.

14:23.440 --> 14:24.210
You're sharp-witted.

14:24.800 --> 14:25.810
Knowing Duantu was dangerous,

14:26.510 --> 14:27.490
why did you not flee?

14:27.920 --> 14:30.260
First, the city gates were heavily guarded.

14:30.590 --> 14:31.570
I dared not risk it.

14:32.710 --> 14:33.330
Second,

14:34.320 --> 14:37.140
I trusted Your Highness would come to our rescue.

14:37.800 --> 14:40.020
Thus, I hid here with Jingwu,

14:40.400 --> 14:41.490
waiting for Your Highness's return.

14:44.350 --> 14:45.690
Uncle, you're back.

14:45.710 --> 14:47.940
Can we rescue my father?

14:52.440 --> 14:53.420
It's my fault for failing you.

14:56.510 --> 14:57.850
I'll spare no effort

14:58.630 --> 14:59.490
to defend the Yue State

15:00.990 --> 15:02.180
and never let your father down again.

15:38.080 --> 15:39.090
Still no breakthrough.

15:39.800 --> 15:41.610
Why can't I break through the third level?

15:50.040 --> 15:51.570
Weighed down by mortal attachments,

15:51.990 --> 15:53.730
you cannot cut off all affection and desire.

15:54.320 --> 15:56.090
The third level is incredibly hard to break through.

15:56.830 --> 15:58.780
Only with heavenly and earthly treasures

15:58.800 --> 16:00.300
and purest spirit energy

16:00.510 --> 16:03.140
might you stand a slim chance.

16:08.990 --> 16:10.380
Purest spirit energy?

16:36.320 --> 16:37.490
Why would you take your own life?

16:37.960 --> 16:39.180
I had no thought of dying.

16:40.080 --> 16:42.450
I want to return to the palace, slay the villains,

16:42.920 --> 16:43.810
and avenge His Majesty.

16:45.040 --> 16:46.730
The palace is swarming with Longming Sanctuary's disciples.

16:47.590 --> 16:49.900
What can a frail girl like you accomplish?

16:50.200 --> 16:51.690
I grew up by the water

16:51.920 --> 16:52.810
and excel at swimming.

16:53.440 --> 16:54.690
Before I left Lugong Town,

16:55.080 --> 16:57.380
Mr. Yan gave me immortal cultivation manuals.

16:57.560 --> 16:58.570
I know a few spirit arts

16:58.710 --> 16:59.450
to protect myself.

17:00.510 --> 17:02.380
I'm just nobody.

17:02.830 --> 17:04.900
At worst, I'll take them down with me.

17:05.320 --> 17:06.610
I can still be of some use.

17:09.990 --> 17:11.580
I only saved you on a whim once.

17:12.310 --> 17:13.450
No need to sacrifice yourself.

17:15.270 --> 17:16.660
I've endured hardship since childhood.

17:17.550 --> 17:19.180
Though I entered Yange Hall,

17:19.880 --> 17:22.290
I was merely an ant, unnoticed by all.

17:22.840 --> 17:23.970
Only that day,

17:25.160 --> 17:26.820
Your Highness saved me

17:27.400 --> 17:28.420
and treated me like a human being.

17:30.230 --> 17:31.140
From then on,

17:32.100 --> 17:34.900
my life belongs to Your Highness.

17:36.400 --> 17:39.290
My only wish is to repay your kindness.

17:40.070 --> 17:41.140
I would die without regret.

17:47.600 --> 17:48.820
Too many have perished already.

17:50.640 --> 17:51.450
I want you to live.

17:52.340 --> 17:53.100
From this moment,

17:54.200 --> 17:55.100
your life is mine.

17:57.550 --> 17:58.380
Without my order,

17:59.640 --> 18:01.050
never act recklessly again.

18:12.440 --> 18:12.940
Tongzhou,

18:13.200 --> 18:14.940
Lu and I will rush to join you

18:15.200 --> 18:16.180
to defeat Zong Quan together.

18:23.440 --> 18:24.180
Tonghe,

18:25.100 --> 18:25.770
Uncle,

18:27.750 --> 18:29.380
now I know my duty.

18:30.470 --> 18:31.620
I'll never fail you again.

18:33.990 --> 18:35.690
I shall master the Xuanhua Sacred Fire soon,

18:36.270 --> 18:37.340
support Jingwu,

18:38.270 --> 18:39.490
and guard the Yue State

18:40.710 --> 18:41.970
for thousands of generations.

18:54.160 --> 18:54.660
Tongzhou,

18:55.840 --> 18:56.970
is your injury flaring up again?

18:58.710 --> 18:59.290
Stay still.

19:20.470 --> 19:21.530
I'm breaking through the third level.

19:22.470 --> 19:23.730
This spirit energy truly works wonders.

19:30.550 --> 19:31.180
Lifei,

19:32.030 --> 19:32.660
are you okay?

19:33.710 --> 19:34.210
I'm fine.

19:35.270 --> 19:36.620
How's your injury?

19:38.790 --> 19:39.450
My bad.

19:40.070 --> 19:41.660
I made you waste too much spirit energy on me.

19:43.600 --> 19:44.100
No big deal.

19:45.270 --> 19:46.530
I have the spirit power of Achillea Bead,

19:46.550 --> 19:47.530
a supreme treasure.

19:47.880 --> 19:49.050
It's endless.

19:50.200 --> 19:50.970
Instead,

19:51.340 --> 19:53.340
you just healed up. Stay cautious.

19:57.880 --> 19:59.690
The Dizang Sect won't get involved in Yue's trouble.

20:00.070 --> 20:01.660
Master locked Ye and me in.

20:01.680 --> 20:02.900
We can't leave the sect.

20:03.440 --> 20:04.690
We're trying to escape.

20:07.790 --> 20:09.490
Can't believe the Longming Sanctuary acts cruelly

20:10.340 --> 20:11.820
yet other sects just stand there scared.

20:14.070 --> 20:15.100
This is always how the immortal sects act.

20:15.640 --> 20:16.490
To the immortal sects,

20:17.400 --> 20:19.010
the rise and fall of mortal states

20:19.030 --> 20:19.820
are trivial matters.

20:20.960 --> 20:22.100
They never lift a finger to interfere.

20:23.200 --> 20:24.140
No one helped

20:24.680 --> 20:25.970
when Gaolu was destroyed.

20:26.510 --> 20:28.770
They're cold and selfish. It's not surprising.

20:29.510 --> 20:30.900
Zong Quan practices evil arts and turns evil.

20:31.340 --> 20:33.900
Why don't all the mountain sect masters stop him?

20:35.680 --> 20:36.940
Every sect only cares for its own troubles.

20:38.510 --> 20:39.660
None will step forward.

20:40.470 --> 20:41.420
We can only rely on ourselves.

20:43.070 --> 20:45.250
Slaying Zong Quan is my fight.

20:53.200 --> 20:54.050
All of you, leave.

20:54.710 --> 20:55.770
Don't risk offending the immortal sects for my sake.

20:56.550 --> 20:58.250
Zong Quan and the Longming Sanctuary are our shared foes.

20:58.750 --> 21:00.050
We will not stand idly by.

21:00.470 --> 21:01.730
His cultivation is formidable now.

21:02.230 --> 21:04.100
The odds are stacked against us. We stand no chance.

21:05.030 --> 21:06.010
I don't want to drag you down.

21:06.750 --> 21:08.140
Stop talking nonsense.

21:08.470 --> 21:09.450
At this critical moment,

21:09.710 --> 21:11.290
we have to join hands to devise a plan.

21:11.920 --> 21:12.490
Besides,

21:12.790 --> 21:14.250
Zong Quan is not who he once was,

21:14.270 --> 21:15.490
nor are we.

21:15.750 --> 21:17.530
If we fight again, we may not lose.

21:49.270 --> 21:50.580
When you went to worship with Tongzhou,

21:51.120 --> 21:52.180
did you drain your spirit power

21:52.840 --> 21:53.690
to heal his injuries again?

21:55.600 --> 21:57.380
His deep grief injured his heart meridians.

22:01.550 --> 22:03.660
I'm fine, just a little tired.

22:41.100 --> 22:41.690
Xiuyuan.

22:49.510 --> 22:50.770
If this happens again,

22:52.200 --> 22:52.940
let me do it.

22:54.840 --> 22:56.250
I'm truly alright.

22:57.960 --> 22:59.530
Strangely enough,

23:00.510 --> 23:01.900
ever since we left the White Cliff,

23:03.160 --> 23:05.340
my spirit power seems to be endless.

23:07.550 --> 23:08.210
Xiuyuan,

23:08.990 --> 23:10.140
is something wrong with me?

23:16.600 --> 23:17.660
Just cultivation progress.

23:18.470 --> 23:19.140
Don't overthink it.

23:24.160 --> 23:25.900
I redrew the Demon-Subduing Formation.

23:26.270 --> 23:27.690
You know formations well.

23:28.070 --> 23:28.970
Help me fix its flaws.

23:30.470 --> 23:31.970
Even if formations are complex,

23:32.640 --> 23:34.620
if the two parties' strengths fall far behind,

23:34.920 --> 23:35.660
it won't work.

23:36.840 --> 23:37.620
Our top priority

23:38.200 --> 23:39.620
is to ambush Zong Quan

23:40.470 --> 23:41.140
while he's injured.

23:41.680 --> 23:42.450
Is he injured?

23:43.400 --> 23:44.860
He didn't appear when Lanya

23:45.550 --> 23:46.490
tried to trap us.

23:47.160 --> 23:50.290
It must be his cultivation deviation.

23:52.440 --> 23:53.420
Fell into demonic possession?

23:54.880 --> 23:55.860
That's not right.

23:56.750 --> 23:58.420
He always practices demonic arts.

23:59.230 --> 24:00.340
Every art has weaknesses,

24:00.920 --> 24:01.530
and everyone's

24:01.880 --> 24:03.290
spirit power differs.

24:03.790 --> 24:05.690
Zong Quan steals others' power

24:06.470 --> 24:07.250
and needs to refine it.

24:07.990 --> 24:08.530
I think

24:09.070 --> 24:11.100
Elder Xuanshan released Burning Flame power

24:11.340 --> 24:12.340
before he died,

24:12.680 --> 24:13.620
which backfired on Zong Quan.

24:14.990 --> 24:15.690
Xiuyuan,

24:17.200 --> 24:18.420
how do you know so much?

24:19.270 --> 24:21.820
I read more books than you.

24:46.160 --> 24:48.010
The Spirit-Devouring Canon is from the Primordial Era.

24:48.310 --> 24:50.860
You can't master it in a short time.

24:51.710 --> 24:53.250
You just destroyed Xingzheng Hall

24:53.440 --> 24:55.340
and absorbed many cultivators' power.

24:55.680 --> 24:56.770
Don't push too hard.

24:57.230 --> 24:59.210
My chest has ached recently.

25:00.470 --> 25:05.340
Is Rakshasa's life talisman acting up?

25:05.790 --> 25:06.490
Let me check.

25:12.550 --> 25:15.210
Zong Quan, you're asking for death!

25:26.200 --> 25:27.420
You refined the Burning Flame!

25:31.200 --> 25:32.900
With Xuanshanzi's Burning Flame

25:33.030 --> 25:34.530
and the Spirit-Devouring Demonic Arts,

25:35.160 --> 25:37.210
I'll become immortal soon.

25:37.600 --> 25:39.970
I won't be the demon clan's

25:39.990 --> 25:41.050
puppet anymore.

25:50.510 --> 25:51.660
The Guardian used Zong Quan

25:51.920 --> 25:52.860
to divide the immortal sects,

25:53.340 --> 25:55.010
but he broke free from the life talisman

25:55.270 --> 25:56.180
and became a huge threat.

25:57.600 --> 25:59.770
Does he have any weak points?

26:00.470 --> 26:01.010
Uh...

26:01.960 --> 26:02.380
Answer me!

26:02.640 --> 26:03.530
I don't know.

26:03.880 --> 26:05.530
But Demon Lord Yecha's supreme power

26:05.750 --> 26:07.970
can cut his spirit root and kill immortals.

26:10.550 --> 26:11.530
Go warn Rakshasa

26:11.990 --> 26:12.820
to watch her step.

26:24.920 --> 26:25.250
Hurry.

26:27.750 --> 26:28.140
Capture him!

26:33.470 --> 26:34.580
Zhao Mingli?

26:35.960 --> 26:36.970
It's you.

26:37.400 --> 26:39.660
Lanya, you killed Zhijie

26:39.920 --> 26:41.010
and His Highness.

26:41.340 --> 26:42.530
I'm going to avenge them.

26:42.790 --> 26:44.940
What's wrong with Tongzhou?

26:45.340 --> 26:46.770
His Highness's injuries were fatal.

26:47.750 --> 26:48.420
He's...

26:49.440 --> 26:50.380
He's dead.

26:51.680 --> 26:52.340
That's a lie!

26:52.640 --> 26:53.860
He would never die.

26:54.070 --> 26:55.530
I wish it weren't true.

26:56.070 --> 26:58.690
Zhijie and His Highness are both gone.

26:58.990 --> 27:00.820
Is this what you wanted, Lanya?

27:01.640 --> 27:02.210
Where's

27:03.100 --> 27:04.250
Tongzhou's body?

27:04.640 --> 27:07.180
At the Orchid Pavilion, north of the city.

27:09.990 --> 27:10.660
Orchid Pavilion.

27:12.150 --> 27:17.800
[Orchid Pavilion]

27:22.230 --> 27:23.730
Tongzhou. Tongzhou.

27:24.400 --> 27:25.620
I knew you weren't dead.

27:26.200 --> 27:26.730
Tongzhou,

27:27.200 --> 27:28.660
don't hate me.

27:29.270 --> 27:30.770
I never wanted to hurt you. Really.

27:32.270 --> 27:33.970
Zong Quan made me do it.

27:38.200 --> 27:38.860
Tongzhou.

27:43.160 --> 27:44.380
What did they make you do?

27:53.070 --> 27:54.450
Zong Quan took me captive

27:55.510 --> 27:57.250
when my parents died for the country.

27:57.600 --> 27:59.660
He put a Gu seal on me

28:02.550 --> 28:04.490
before we reached Duantu to control me,

28:05.470 --> 28:07.100
so I have to follow his orders.

28:13.710 --> 28:14.580
Is this Longming Seal?

28:18.070 --> 28:19.770
It tortures me with worm pain

28:20.550 --> 28:22.290
whenever I disobey him.

28:23.470 --> 28:24.530
It's unbearable.

28:27.840 --> 28:28.380
Tongzhou,

28:30.070 --> 28:31.940
I never wanted to hurt Tonghe

28:32.200 --> 28:33.940
or Mr. Xuanshan.

28:34.470 --> 28:37.180
But if I refused Zong Quan,

28:37.600 --> 28:38.860
he'd kill you.

28:39.710 --> 28:40.210
Tongzhou,

28:40.710 --> 28:42.660
I only acted to protect you.

28:43.120 --> 28:44.770
My feelings for you never changed.

28:45.160 --> 28:46.450
I swear. I never lied.

28:46.470 --> 28:47.660
Trust me.

28:53.160 --> 28:53.690
Tongzhou.

28:56.990 --> 28:59.770
If you really want to help me,

29:02.120 --> 29:03.290
kill Zong Quan.

29:11.640 --> 29:12.340
Tongzhou,

29:16.750 --> 29:17.770
do you hate me?

29:24.400 --> 29:25.530
I'd be lying if I said no.

29:26.310 --> 29:27.690
You killed my uncle

29:28.230 --> 29:29.050
and betrayed me.

29:33.790 --> 29:34.380
But

29:35.840 --> 29:37.690
I've always regarded you as my family.

29:38.680 --> 29:40.490
Right now, I can rely only on you.

29:41.120 --> 29:41.660
Lanya,

29:42.960 --> 29:44.290
kill Zong Quan,

29:45.750 --> 29:47.660
and we'll forget everything that happened before.

29:52.200 --> 29:53.210
What about Jiang Lifei?

29:56.070 --> 29:57.180
Won't she help you?

30:03.680 --> 30:05.250
She only cares about Lei Xiuyuan.

30:06.790 --> 30:08.530
Gelin and the others

30:09.440 --> 30:12.010
are too weak to help much anyway.

30:21.270 --> 30:21.770
Help me,

30:22.960 --> 30:23.620
Lanya.

30:25.200 --> 30:26.420
After I kill Zong Quan

30:27.470 --> 30:28.490
and become emperor,

30:29.960 --> 30:31.250
you'll be my empress.

30:36.470 --> 30:37.420
Then nobody

30:38.230 --> 30:39.580
can threaten you anymore.

30:40.440 --> 30:43.490
We'll work together to rebuild the Yue State.

30:56.960 --> 30:58.580
How can I prove I'm sincere?

31:13.440 --> 31:15.010
This is a Heartbound Gu.

31:15.880 --> 31:16.730
Take it,

31:18.440 --> 31:19.820
and we'll live or die together.

31:32.680 --> 31:33.380
Tongzhou.

31:54.990 --> 31:55.820
Keep Jingwu safe.

31:56.200 --> 31:57.940
If you hear nothing by Chen hour,

31:58.200 --> 31:59.180
leave Duantu right away.

31:59.790 --> 32:02.010
Go to Fengchu Academy for Mr. Zuo Qiu.

32:04.750 --> 32:05.450
Don't worry, Your Highness.

32:06.030 --> 32:07.730
I'll finish what you asked,

32:08.120 --> 32:08.820
no matter the cost.

32:10.310 --> 32:12.340
Uncle, focus on your mission.

32:12.960 --> 32:14.290
I've grown up,

32:14.310 --> 32:15.690
and I can take care of myself.

32:20.510 --> 32:21.420
Be a good boy.

32:25.270 --> 32:25.820
Go now.

32:26.880 --> 32:28.050
Your Royal Highness, let's go.

32:54.230 --> 32:54.770
Understood.

32:58.120 --> 32:59.140
What's wrong, Your Ladyship?

32:59.510 --> 33:00.860
Drinking to forget your pain?

33:03.310 --> 33:04.660
Tongzhou must hate me.

33:05.750 --> 33:09.490
I have no one left in this world.

33:10.710 --> 33:12.250
My life is meaningless.

33:15.360 --> 33:16.970
Tongzhou is gone,

33:17.750 --> 33:19.250
but I'm still here for you.

33:23.030 --> 33:23.860
Senior Brother.

33:48.550 --> 33:49.620
I knew you were plotting something.

33:50.550 --> 33:51.770
You're useless now.

33:52.510 --> 33:53.530
Meet your end.

33:58.710 --> 33:59.340
Lu Li?

34:00.960 --> 34:01.860
Gelin sent me to help you.

34:02.440 --> 34:03.860
Another fool begging to die.

34:04.510 --> 34:06.900
Fine, I'll send you both off.

34:25.840 --> 34:26.860
What's this?

34:27.220 --> 34:28.610
Instant-kill poison.

34:29.110 --> 34:29.900
You're getting off easy.

34:39.920 --> 34:41.900
Father, he is ahead.

34:42.280 --> 34:43.450
Must be the doing of Jiang Lifei's group.

35:31.470 --> 35:33.220
Fighting back desperately?

35:33.510 --> 35:35.420
I'll finish you off!

35:43.220 --> 35:44.610
The Sea Sect's Evasive Talisman Technique.

36:02.590 --> 36:04.340
You're way better now.

36:30.590 --> 36:31.860
Yecha's supreme power

36:32.220 --> 36:34.420
can cut his spirit root and kill immortals.

36:40.760 --> 36:41.420
Demon.

37:07.800 --> 37:09.420
The Divine Tree's spirit aura.

37:10.670 --> 37:12.220
You're the Divine Tree!

37:48.550 --> 37:49.970
You're the Divine Tree!

37:57.150 --> 37:57.820
Master,

37:58.190 --> 38:00.820
why do those spirits keep pestering me?

38:01.110 --> 38:01.900
Because

38:02.320 --> 38:04.490
they love your sweet scent.

38:04.990 --> 38:05.820
Sweet scent?

38:22.590 --> 38:23.450
Five centuries ago,

38:23.700 --> 38:26.450
Demon Lord Yecha was obsessed with the Divine Tree.

38:26.990 --> 38:29.130
Couldn't have it, so he tried to destroy it.

38:43.070 --> 38:44.260
According to the surviving guards,

38:44.840 --> 38:46.530
Zong Quan threw captured Xingzheng Hall disciples here

38:46.990 --> 38:48.010
to absorb their power.

38:49.150 --> 38:50.820
All were thrown in alive.

38:51.510 --> 38:53.700
Their broken souls fill this place with rage.

38:54.670 --> 38:56.300
Plus Zong Quan's demonic spirit,

38:56.920 --> 38:59.570
this altar became a soul-slaughtering purgatory.

39:00.670 --> 39:01.970
Ordinary people can't get close.

39:02.990 --> 39:04.170
I don't know what to do.

39:04.990 --> 39:06.940
Lei Xiuyuan, you're stronger.

39:07.670 --> 39:08.820
Can you purify this place?

39:16.190 --> 39:16.820
Don't come closer.

39:18.920 --> 39:19.940
The demonic energy may corrupt you.

39:21.880 --> 39:22.700
I'll take care of it.

39:23.440 --> 39:24.050
Go handle other things.

39:25.800 --> 39:26.650
I'll count on you.

39:50.400 --> 39:51.170
Lifei,

39:52.150 --> 39:53.420
you should rest in your room.

39:54.460 --> 39:55.170
Feeling better?

39:57.070 --> 39:57.780
Yes, I'm okay.

40:02.760 --> 40:05.530
Can they never reincarnate?

40:06.590 --> 40:07.380
Hatred lingers after death.

40:08.470 --> 40:09.530
Their souls

40:11.110 --> 40:11.970
won't let go.

40:12.670 --> 40:14.490
I have to block it with a formation

40:15.190 --> 40:16.530
to keep ordinary people safe.

40:17.900 --> 40:18.860
They'll be trapped here forever

40:19.860 --> 40:20.780
with no way out.

40:22.300 --> 40:23.530
How tragic for them.

40:27.670 --> 40:28.780
Let's go to Tongzhou.

40:29.510 --> 40:31.860
The Xuanhua Sacred Fire might clear their hatred.

40:40.380 --> 40:41.340
If they can be cleared

40:42.820 --> 40:43.700
and start over,

40:44.900 --> 40:46.010
that'll be the best result.

41:36.990 --> 41:37.530
Jingwu,

41:38.190 --> 41:39.900
after your coronation three days later,

41:40.340 --> 41:41.530
you'll be the emperor

41:42.340 --> 41:44.530
and carry the Yue State on your shoulders.

41:45.470 --> 41:48.010
I'm too young and unlearned.

41:48.030 --> 41:50.050
You should be the emperor.

41:54.980 --> 41:56.050
I've joined the immortal sect

41:56.720 --> 41:59.610
and will be Xingzheng Hall's Immortal Lord soon.

42:00.470 --> 42:01.170
Don't worry.

42:01.670 --> 42:03.300
I'll always back you up,

42:03.990 --> 42:04.740
just like

42:07.300 --> 42:09.970
my uncle supported your father.

42:10.920 --> 42:12.610
How dare you stop me!

42:13.280 --> 42:14.130
How dare you!

42:15.070 --> 42:16.010
Sorry, Your Ladyship.

42:16.400 --> 42:17.300
His Majesty forbids

42:17.590 --> 42:18.780
anyone from entering.

42:19.380 --> 42:20.130
You?

42:22.510 --> 42:26.450
You're the maid who took Jingwu away!

42:29.190 --> 42:31.260
I'm Miaoqing. Greetings, Your Ladyship.

42:33.980 --> 42:36.900
Insulting nobility is punishable by death.

42:37.940 --> 42:38.900
Drag her off and flog her to death.

42:38.940 --> 42:39.340
- Yes. - Yes.

42:39.360 --> 42:39.900
Wait!

42:42.050 --> 42:42.360
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.360 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
